  <div id="text-content_7AEB61C0-1EF9-0135-F603-22000B5A851D" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Select the name of the student you'd like to message [1]. </p>
<p>To message all students in the student group, click the <strong>All in Student Group</strong> link [2].</p>
  </div>
